Wrapped up an incredible session at All About Music in Mumbai, where I had the privilege of moderating a discussion on ‘Evolving Relationships Between Music Creators and Platforms.’

It was truly enriching to share the stage with such talented panelists: Justh (singer-songwriter of the hit song ‘Chor’), Rajant from YouTube, Sunder Venketraman from Josh, Edwin Albert from Airtel Digital Wykn, and Rahul Khanna from Barcode.

I’m grateful for the opportunity to share insights and connect with so many passionate professionals. A huge thank you to everyone who joined us and contributed to the conversation! 🎶✨

latestPosts.caption:
Excited to be back at All About Music in Mumbai! 🎶 

I’ve been part of this incredible event since its inception, and tomorrow, August 6th, I’ll be moderating a panel at 2 PM IST.

Join me as we discuss ‘Harmonizing the Future: Evolving Relationships Between Music Creators and Platforms’ with an amazing lineup of panelists: Justh (singer-songwriter of the hit song ‘Chor’), Rajant from YouTube, Edwin Albert from Airtel Digital Wykn, Sunder Venketraman from Josh, and Rahul Khanna from Barcode.

Got questions? Drop them in the comments, and we might just ask them during the panel! 🎤 

We’ll dive into the importance of collaboration between music creators and platforms and explore their perspectives on the future.

Justh - Singer-Songwriter
Edwin Albert - AVP & Head Content Partnership, Airtel Digital 
Sunder Venketraman - Head of Content, Creator Monetisation Ecosystem Josh & Verse Innovation 
Rajant Meshram - Head of Artist & Label Development (APAC) YouTube
Rahul Khanna Founder & Director Barcode Entertainment

@youtubemusic @officialjoshapp @wynkmusic @barcodeent

🎶 Exciting News on the Horizon! 🌟
We are thrilled to announce that Nexa Music Season 3 is officially underway, and this time, we’re going multilingual! This project holds a special place in our hearts at Qyuki as we aim to transcend the norms of IP creation, nurture emerging talent, and redefine music marketing across languages.
Nexa Music Season 3 is a testament to our unwavering dedication, bringing together exceptional talent and groundbreaking musical experiences like never before, now in multiple languages. This season, we’re elevating the experience with a diverse range of tracks and mesmerizing performances that showcase the pinnacle of our creative endeavors.
🔥 Stay tuned for a season that not only promises to captivate your senses but also aims to redefine the standards of innovative musical experiences across linguistic boundaries. We’re here to make history, and we invite you to be a part of this groundbreaking journey.
👉 Keep an eye on our channels for updates, behind-the-scenes sneak peeks, and more surprises along the way!
